name: Through obstacles
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting. 1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko & I'll send you the painting!

Through obstacles
Preparing to paint a new artwork, I bought sprays, canvas, tools. I had no idea that a new adventure awaited me.
When working with sprays, everything happens incredibly fast, it's always the maximum presence and inclusion, because I have a window of time until everything is dry.
When I started working, I noticed that one of the paints has amazing properties. First, the paint is as thick as spaghetti and dries 10 times faster, it added too much thickener.
Here I had to do the impossible, and I managed to do everything I could.
It's fun to discover new resources where familiar scenarios end.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2017, 80x80 cm, spray paint on canvas, 2901x2891 pix.
